50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用visual studio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2f102ea9293b3fc68eaed7f226bbb083110d8f","tid":1110331,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bc7d1ead5a9ab59c6e57f31e94e15511f90ac27","tid":1110331,"uid":98317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"話用intellij既多數係仲讀緊書，係現實間間公司用Eclipse"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為比唔起license<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb0a62259d724df332e8910203c1c5656aae6cc","tid":1110331,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc2f102ea9293b3fc68eaed7f226bbb083110d8f","tid":1110331,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bc7d1ead5a9ab59c6e57f31e94e15511f90ac27","tid":1110331,"uid":98317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"話用intellij既多數係仲讀緊書，係現實間間公司用Eclipse"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為比唔起license<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"兩個IDE都本人有用, 各有各好處.<br />\n話intellij要錢的....佢有唔使錢的community版. 還是工作上非要用到要俾錢的features不可?<br />\n排除錢呢個因素. 講方便的話Eclipse係方便D. 因為&quot;唔使裝&quot;,爆開個zip就用得. 係D 冇admin right的機做野方便好多(出來做嘢就會知道, 一間公司要grant local admin right有幾難/煩), 唔使下下都要搵admin出來開admin right俾你裝嘢.<br />\nP.S: D security係唔撚會明, 對developer而言local admin有幾重要. 冇local admin好多dev tool都用唔到, 疑人不用, 用人不疑. 一間公司真係信唔過員工, 覺得佢會亂用local admin right的話就幹脆唔好請佢. 請完人番來然後就挷手挷腳, 條友再勁都唔會曉飛的."},{"pid":"5ab88abd6f7e389e219fa7fe171af7ada8dbf464","tid":1110331,"uid":145277,"like"